aboutUs.title: About scentQ
aboutUs.paragraph1: Do you ever faced the problem of testing and buying a perfume at the store but after that realizing that the perfume is not suitable at all. This is because testing perfume at the store, does not capture how the perfume evolves with your daily routine when you start wearing it. Do you also find yourself limited by your perfume?
aboutUs.paragraph2: That is why ScentQ was founded. ScentQ is a monthly subscription based service that allows you to choose from hundreds of designer fragrances and delivers a 30- day supply right to your doorstep and making it easier and more enjoyable for individuals to explore and enjoy a variety of scents tailored to their preferences
aboutUs.missionStatement: ScentQ passion revolves around spreading happiness through the power of fragrance. Our goal is to transform the way people experience fragrance by providing an exceptional fragrance park right to their doorstep.
fragranceDiscoveryDescription: ScentQ makes fragrance selection easy. We offer an affordable way to sample scents before committing to a full bottle, addressing the challenge of compatibility with body chemistry and preferences.
costlyFullSizedBottlesDescription: Avoid costly mistakes with full-size perfume bottles. ScentQ lets subscribers sample scents before making a commitment to a full-size purchase.
convenienceDescription: Don't lug around a full-size perfume bottle. ScentQ's travel-sized atomizer offers a convenient way to carry and apply fragrance on the go.
personalizationDescription: ScentQ refines choices with customer ratings, providing tailored suggestions that match unique preferences.
limitedAccessToNicheScentsDescription: ScentQ provides access to a diverse range of mainstream and niche fragrances that may not be readily available in local stores.
anaxanimDescription: Anaxanim the visionary founder and CEO of ScentQ is a visionary entrepreneur who has transformed the way people experience and access fragrances. With an unwavering passion for scents and a deep understanding of consumer preferences, Anaxanim embarked on a mission to democratize luxury fragrances. Under Anaxanim's leadership, ScentQ has flourished offering a curated selection of exquisite fragrances delivered directly to customers' doorsteps, elevating the olfactory experience for thousands of subscribers worldwide. Anaxanim continues to drive innovation and elevate the fragrance subscription industry, making luxury scents more accessible and enjoyable for customers around the world.
orkhanDescription: As the founder and COO of ScentQ, Orkhan brings invaluable expertise in operations and strategic management to the company. With a proven track record of optimizing supply chains and enhancing customer experiences, Orkhan has been instrumental in the company's rapid growth and success. His dedication to ensuring seamless subscription fulfillment and exceptional service has solidified ScentQ’s position as a top player in the fragrance industry. Orkhan continues to drive operational excellence and innovation, ensuring that subscribers receive their favorite fragrances with efficiency and reliability.

What is the queue and how does it work?: What is the queue and how does it work?
As a ScentQ subscriber, you have complet: As a ScentQ subscriber, you have complete control over the contents of your monthly shipment. You can easily select items from our collection and arrange them in the order you prefer within your queue. After that, we handle the rest.  Once your order enters the processing phase, changes cannot be made, as it is being prepared for shipment. However, you are welcome to adjust your queue for future month's shipments at any time!
